<div id="porf-col" class="col-sm-6">
    <p>
	<li>
	<a href="https://thewterclone.herokuapp.com" target="_blank">Thewter Clone</a> is a primitive twitter clone that has basic website functionalities and basic twitter functionalities. This App is built in Rails following conventions implemented in various Ruby gems:
	<ul>
	    <li>
		using password digest stored as hashes instead of saving the actual password in the PostgresSQL database.
	    </li>
	    <li>
		uses Carrierwave for uploading images and  mini_magick for resizing the image to a manageable size, then saving them to a AWS bucket.
	    </li>
	    <li>
		Used a Test Driven Approach by using Minitest, and created fake users using Faker.
	    </li>
	</ul>
    </li>
    </p>
</div>
<div class="col-sm-6">
    <div id="tcCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
	<!-- Indicators -->
	<ol class="carousel-indicators">
